# Intern Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get my progress (protected, for intern)
GET http://localhost:3001/interns/me/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get intern progress by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/interns/{{id}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create intern profile (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/interns
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "userId": "<user-id>",
  "mentorId": "<mentor-id>",
  "candidateId": "<candidate-id>",
  "track": "BACKEND",
  "startDate": "2026-04-01"
}

### Get all interns (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/interns
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get intern by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/interns/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update intern (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/interns/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

### Delete intern (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/interns/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
